casebody.data:
JOSEPH DICKERSON, PROSECUTOR, v. JOSEPH ALTMAN, RECORDER OF ATLANTIC CITY, RESPONDENT. Submitted August 14, 1934 Decided October 6, 1934.

Before Justices Teen chard, Hei-ier and Perskie.

For the prosecutor-petitioner, Samuel Morris. For the respondent, Anthony J. Siracusa. Per Curiam.

The petition of the prosecutor for a rehearing is denied.

See Dickerson v. Altman, 12 N. J. Mis. R. 656; 174 Atl. Rep. 207.
